author: Chris Tomlinson
title: Egyptian Migrant Who Sexually Assaulted 14-year-old Should Have Been Deported in 2011
text: A 21-year-old Egyptian man has been arrested following accusations that he sexually assaulted a 14-year-old girl in an asylum home despite the fact that he was rejected for asylum since 2011 and authorities have been trying to deport him for five years.
